Usage: reportCritNet [-help] [-nrCritNets <interger>] [-outfile <fileName>]
                     [-targetSlack <double>] [-view <viewName>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-nrCritNets <interger>  # number of critical nets (int, optional)
-outfile <fileName>     # Output file name (string, optional)
-targetSlack <double>   # targetSlack (float, optional)
-view <viewName>        # view name (string, optional)